ked nation\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"the first country\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"morethan 30 medals\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The officialOlympicswebsite meanwhile has China in first place with 11 golds, and the US languishing down the table below Australia, Japan and hosts France.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8766930732884118, \"rank\": 0.13770252926073093, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999370113971809, \"rank\": 5.9075341001924966e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.6715356203323548, \"rank\": 0.36610834065712655, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6083648217043433, \"rank\": 0.6001667153557222, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The officialOlympicswebsite\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"first place\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"11 golds\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American media argue it is a method that has been deployed for decades, but it remains a point of contention at each Games.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999541147012903, \"rank\": 4.163196562860729e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a method\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"each Games\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, in the actual medal table, the US are 6th.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999370113971809, \"rank\": 5.9075341001924966e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the actual medal table\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Love that they have turned comments off as they know they are wrong.#Paris2024https://t.co/2cKGj99iy1pic.twitter.com/MUTBlI3IkE \\\"The New York Times is better than this, but they always do it,\\\" tweeted Nick Bryant, author and former Washington correspondent for the BBC.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The