d\\u2026\\u2026\\\" Some responses defended the Times' method, writing: \\\"You are just noticing this?\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_exceptionalism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American exceptionalism\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_exceptionalism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_exceptionalism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mad\\u2026\\u2026\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"Some responses\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"the Times' method\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been the metal count methodology for at least 25 years now.\\\"\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the metal count methodology\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 25 years\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian journalist Bradley Jurd tweeted: \\\"Every country in the world ranks by gold medals.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.6515266288172605, \"rank\": 0.4177891630158972, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Braves_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.5059863297969281, \"rank\": 0.716745540934491, \"text\": \"Bradley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Braves_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Braves_men's_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every country\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's never by total.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is a country that insists on Fahrenheit and pounds, when almost no one else does.\\\"\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fahrenheit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3050345558256544e-21, \"text\": \"Fahrenheit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fahrenheit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fahrenheit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"pounds\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"almost no one\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC has sometimes turned comments off on X when tweeting out the medal count, but that has not stopped the scrutiny.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.6102933173301011, \"rank\": 0.6374166025202163, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal count\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"the scrutiny\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Meanwhile, in the actual medal table, the US are 6th,\\\" quote-tweeted one user.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2658, \"end\": 2660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999370113971809, \"rank\": 5.9075341001924966e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the actual medal table\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \",\\\" quote-tweeted one user\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Love that they have turned comments off as they know they are wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Love\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another wrote: \\\"Again the US media opt for their own feel good sort rules for the medal table vs the official table.\\\"\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999370113971809, \"rank\": 5.9075341001924966e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"good sort rules\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal table\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the official table\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American media needn't have worried in Tokyo, eventually edging out China by one gold to top the table whichever way it was presented.\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 3020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999541147012903, \"rank\": 4.163196562860729e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2